## ğŸ“– Overview

Welcome to **DevOps Agent Dora** â€” a self-built, modular, and intelligent agent designed to track and optimize your team's **DORA metrics** using modern DevOps and AI principles. This project integrates performance data from your CI/CD systems and operational environments to surface engineering insights with real impact.

ğŸ“Š DORA Metrics Tracked:
